text: Schonungen is a municipality in Schweinfurt, Bavaria, Germany. The villages in this municipality are: *Schonungen *Forst (Unterfranken) *Abersfeld *Mainberg *Hausen *Marktsteinach *Loeffelsterz *Reichmannshausen and some more ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Schweinfurt (district)
